  <brief_title>Serum Metal Ion Concentration After Total Knee Arthroplasty (TKA)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Randomized Comparison of Serum Metal Ion Levels After Implantation of Coated and Uncoated Knee Prostheses</official_title>
